org.intermine.bio.dataconversion

Class ModEncodeFeatureProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.ChadoProcessor
      • org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.SequenceProcessor
        • org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.ModEncodeFeatureProcessor

  • public class ModEncodeFeatureProcessor
extends SequenceProcessor
    A processor that loads feature referred to by the modENCODE metadata. This class is designed to be used by ModEncodeMetaDataProcessor and will be called once for each submission that has metadata.

      • getCommonFeaturesMap

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.Integer,org.intermine.bio.dataconversion.FeatureData> getCommonFeaturesMap()
        Get a map of features that are expected to be common between submissions. This map can be used to initialise this processor for a subsequent run. The feature types added to this map are governed by the addToFeatureMap method in this class.
        Returns:
        a map of chado feature id to FeatureData objects

        protected java.lang.String getExtraFeatureConstraint()

        Overrides:
